\lim_{x \rightarrow0}\frac{1}{x^2}
x=0 
\lim_{x \rightarrow 0} f(x)
\lim_{x \rightarrow 0_-} f(x)
\lim_{x \rightarrow 0_+} f(x)
\lim_{x \rightarrow 0_+} f(x)=\lim_{x \rightarrow 0_-} f(x)
\lim_{x \rightarrow 0_+} \frac{1}{x^2}= \infty=\lim_{x \rightarrow 0_-} \frac{1}{x^2}
\lim_{x \rightarrow 0} \frac{1}{x^2}=\infty
\lim_{x \rightarrow 0} \frac{1}{x}
